{"tid":695941,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人隻貓成日係咁叫？","createTime":"2018-06-09T15:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T01:52:50.000Z","uid":154537,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6808fde29e4998ae27396ea83af8656db4911eb0","tid":695941,"uid":154537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:38:52.000Z","msg":"呢隻衰囡成個港女咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日對住我喵喵喵，又唔係無水，又唔係無糧，屎又剷左，就係唔知佢喵乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘係每朝6點開始喵到8點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嘈住我訓覺，一開始想睇乜事，都係個句，有水有糧無屎剷，我宜加已經唔理佢照訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/233015_7207f4932bedddab1222e878c1e698d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F09%2F233015_7207f4932bedddab1222e878c1e698d7.png&h=bc5dd89b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成日扮乜淑女，其實八婆黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/233505_3208d2857fc76122478f3e88109fcf53.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F09%2F233505_3208d2857fc76122478f3e88109fcf53.png&h=bc1de679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n訓到幾鬼麻甩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/233604_d7e3934d202bf1f4013a409e3a3a071f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F09%2F233604_d7e3934d202bf1f4013a409e3a3a071f.png&h=1b6a39d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明明同胎既，細佬又靜又欺文又乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/233817_c3287c809c55283093a4d84832e3a14f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F09%2F233817_c3287c809c55283093a4d84832e3a14f.png&h=4303c8cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ed00347e45928f73facc5ce94237e590b833d0","tid":695941,"uid":104258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"西痕阿"},{"pid":"555b4e768030009c8cbe2fdd3c73e98eb24c6dbb","tid":695941,"uid":154537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8ed00347e45928f73facc5ce94237e590b833d0","tid":695941,"uid":104258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:40:14.000Z","msg":"西痕阿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"閹左啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gi